'''Arram amesguceṛ unɣid''' (Azamul-is: '''RCT''' id yekkan seg [[Taglizit|EN]]: ''Randomised Controlled Trial'') d talmest gar n inawen n unagi ussnan anarum aladɣa deg tɣult n [[tasnujjya|tesnujjya]]. Anda imdanen ɣef wacu id tettili tezrawt [[Tawessna|ttwasennefrun]] s ugucar (s imisi neɣ apipri) s yiwet neɣ ugar n tarrayin n ussuji yemgaraden yettilin deg tezrawt. Dɣa irramen imesgucaṛen unɣiden ttumeggzen d [[akayad n umnir]] deg [[arram ulektu|warramen ilektuyen]] yerna yettwasemres (yettwaseqdec) i wkayad n [[tamellilt|tmellilt]] n inawen yemgaraden n inekcumen isnajjyanen. Akken id yezmer ad yefk isalan ɣef [[tasedmirt tansafart tuɣnift]].

